text: Jacob Batalon (born October 9, 1996) is an American actor. He is best known for his role as Ned Leeds in the Marvel Cinematic Universe movies Spider-Man: Homecoming (2017), Avengers: Infinity War (2018), Avengers: Endgame (2019), Spider-Man: Far From Home (2019), and Spider-Man: No Way Home (2021). Batalon was born in Honolulu, Hawaii.
